title: Nvidia Taps Google Cloud Vet Alison Wagonfeld as First CMO to Fuel AI Growth
description: Nvidia has appointed Alison Wagonfeld, a Google Cloud veteran, as its first chief marketing officer to bolster its AI dominance. Reporting directly to CEO Jensen Huang, she will unify global marketing efforts amid explosive growth. This strategic hire aims to elevate Nvidia's brand beyond tech circles, targeting enterprises and governments.
